<h1>Owners</h1>

<p>Owners are advised not to accept an adoption request without a response to the screening 
questionnaire provided and veterinarian confirmation. Please check your state and local laws for any restrictions regarding ferrets. For example, <em>ferrets are illegal to keep as pets within the 5 boroughs of New York City.</em></p>
<br>

<div>
  <% @owners.each do |owner| %>
    <div class="centering"><h3><%= link_to owner.first_name, owner_path(owner) %>  - <%= owner.quantity %> ferrets</h3></div><br>
  <% end %>
</div>